Sunday 27th July 2014 ITV4
9pm to 10pm Highlights

Highlights of the final day of this year's Tour de France. The peloton process from Evry on the outskirts of Paris onto the iconic Champs-Elysees, where the 2014 Tour de France culminates in a bunch sprint after nine laps of the circuit. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
